spice_template:
.model J201_mod NJF(Vto=-0.8 Beta=1.4e-3 Lambda=2e-3 Is=1e-14)
.subckt TL072_model inp inn out vcc vee
E1 mid 0 inp inn 200000
R1 mid out 100
.ends
* LFO - Schmitt trigger
XU1a tri_fb schmitt_inv sq_out vcc vee TL072_model
Rh1 sq_out tri_fb {{Rh1}}
Rh2 tri_fb bias {{Rh2}}
* LFO - Integrator
XU1b bias int_inv tri_out vcc vee TL072_model
Rint sq_out rate_node {{Rint}}
Rrate rate_node int_inv {{Rrate}}
Cint int_inv tri_out {{Cint}}
* Depth control
Rdepth tri_out depth_wiper {{Rdepth}}
Clfo_filter depth_wiper gnd {{Clfo_filter}}
* LFO to JFET gate
Rbias_lfo depth_wiper gate {{Rbias_lfo}}
* Signal path - JFET VCA
Cin in in_ac {{Cin}}
Rin in_ac drain {{Rin}}
J1 drain gate source J201_mod
R_source source gnd 1k
Cout drain out {{Cout}}
* Bias
Rb1 vcc bias {{Rb1}}
Rb2 bias gnd {{Rb2}}
Cb bias gnd {{Cb}}
Vcc vcc gnd DC {{Vcc}}
